  test_impl,L2,test execution (exitCode=1),false,"TDD Red: 7/7 tests FAIL as expected. All test cases confirm missing functionality.\n\nRUN v1.6.1 - TDD Red Phase: 7 tests, 0 passed, 7 failed\nx error-toon.test.ts > TC-AC1-01: mapChecksForErrorToon is not a function\nx error-toon.test.ts > TC-AC1-02: mapChecksForErrorToon is not a function\nx phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC3-01: expected passed check to be excluded from failure count\nx phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC3-02: expected 'L1' to be 'L3' (level hardcoded)\nx phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC2-01: expected undefined not to be undefined (errorHistory)\nx analytics-toon.test.ts >","2026-03-25T11:31:26.884Z"
  implementation,L2,test execution (exitCode=0),true,"TDD Green: 7/7 tests PASS. tsc clean. lifecycle-next.ts 197 lines.\n\nRUN v1.6.1 - TDD Green Phase: 7 tests, 7 passed, 0 failed (394ms)\n✓ error-toon.test.ts > TC-AC1-01: maps all fields correctly (name,passed,message,level,fix,example)\n✓ error-toon.test.ts > TC-AC1-02: optional fields are undefined when omitted\n✓ phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC3-01: excludes passed=true checks from failure count\n✓ phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC3-02: uses actual check.level instead of hardcoded L1\n✓ phase-analytics.test.ts > TC-AC2-01: flattens all entries and all checks into erro","2026-03-25T11:37:32.695Z"
